{"tid":47083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅硬又順手　陝西漢15年來用手榴彈開合桃","createTime":"2016-12-20T05:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T06:31:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b436bee867165a21cf15a83f61c5183e169a2ec8","tid":47083,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161219/photo/bkncn-20161219224328174-1219_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161219234125\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161219%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161219224328174-1219_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161219234125&h=d7257160&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陝西安康市紫陽縣東木鎮一名冉姓村民日前到派出所，主動向警方上繳其一直用來砸開合桃的「工具」。警方收到後大吃一驚，發現該「工具」竟是一枚67式手榴彈。該手榴彈雖然已經沒有引線裝置，但內部仍可能存有炸藥。 <br />\n<br />\n冉男表示，他25年前在外地工作，獲朋友贈送一個沒有引線的手榴彈。他見該手榴彈頂端鐵塊堅硬，且拿起來相當順手，便一直留在身邊。而在近15年來，他更一直用此來砸合桃。 <br />\n<br />\n早前當地警方推動爆炸品整治專項行動，並向村民派發宣傳單張。冉男才因此意識到該砸合桃的「工具」，也屬於公安機關嚴厲禁止私藏使用的彈藥，於是立即拿到派出所上繳。警方事後鑑於冉男主動上繳並有悔過之心，故只對他進行批評教育。"},{"pid":"9d6dbefdaec756dc7305b1987dadbfdb116be120","tid":47083,"uid":59644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:10:22.000Z","msg":"如果做按摩棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0118acc7a0f5a4cfb160a6ab533801460009129","tid":47083,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"394cabcebd94bdea0fe06bb3b4ca702be0668496","tid":47083,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果做按摩棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀妹，我們再爽一次，哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee362acbd406cd670f5bbd3e375b24e0f08c03d","tid":47083,"uid":7637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"批評教育 鬼國真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a1c889cafefd99d17ea01050f81fc9c0b47943","tid":47083,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為用手榴彈炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fed95a860517decb7ee1f669021daa539d7ee9","tid":47083,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇標題以為用手榴彈炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}